The paper deals with secure communication in a fading channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The proposed scheme involves user cooperation, which is a common theme in networking (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also focuses on massive MIMO, which is a subfield of signal processing and communication (cs.MM).
